          <li><strong>UK261</strong> — UK departures, UK airline arrivals</li>
          <li><strong>APPR</strong> — Canadian departures, arrivals, or Canadian airlines</li>
          <li><strong>Montreal Convention</strong> — most international flights (baggage &amp; delays)</li>
          <li><strong>ANAC 400/2022</strong> — Brazilian flights</li>
          <li><strong>Israel Aviation Services Law</strong> — Israeli flights</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="ec-scope-gap"><strong>Not fully covered:</strong> Purely domestic flights within the US, most Asian countries, Australia, and most of Africa and the Middle East currently have no equivalent fixed-compensation law. If your flight touches Europe, Canada, Brazil, or Israel, you are likely covered.</p>
